{"tid":1168791,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人口不斷膨脹 而陸續有動物絕種/數量減少","createTime":"2019-05-24T02:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T11:34:34.000Z","uid":148749,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a16db71cbe85144d520569de2bd21bd53dd498","tid":1168791,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"呢個世界既靈魂數量係固定既<br />\n因為人類近代不繼大量繁殖 分簿曬其他物種既庫存<br />\n其他物種冇曬spare就自然絕種/數量減少<br />\n<br />\n呢度係講緊靈魂數量唔係資源數量<br />\n就好似熊貓咁有食有住都唔肯生<br />\n就係因為佢庫存啲靈魂比人類搶曬<br />\n佢明知點扑都冇蛋出 不如慳番啖力好過"},{"pid":"bc66dfe6a6d65bbd3861ab09a9d7af6496da23fc","tid":1168791,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 終極合金屬<br />\n唔想再見到你D偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37e3dc0537c1c262eb8c002c7aa48af44aada0c","tid":1168791,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc66dfe6a6d65bbd3861ab09a9d7af6496da23fc","tid":1168791,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 終極合金屬<br />\n唔想再見到你D偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b107b9567c85889c1daa46e9b17695a48f4d7c5e","tid":1168791,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"認真po冇人理"}]}